<% provide(:title, 'About') %>

<div id='about-splash' style="background-image:url('<%= asset_path("about/innovators.jpg") %>')">
  <div class='opacity-layer'>
    <div class="container">

      <p class='splash-title' data-fittext='1.8' data-fittext-min="28" data-fittext-max="48">Seven&bull;zo: A communal effort to make change possible.</p>
      <p class='splash-subtitle' data-fittext='2.4' data-fittext-min="16" data-fittext-max="24">We bring together communities to diffuse what works in education so that all learners can reach their full potential.</p>
      <hr>

      <h2 class='splash-learn' href='#about-story' du-smooth-scroll>
        <span class='text-underline'>Learn More</span>.<br><i class='fa fa-chevron-down'></i>
      </h2>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="about-nav" data-spy="affix" data-offset-top="315" class="affix-top">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row about-nav-links">
      <div class='col-xs-2 about-nav-link' href='#about-story' du-smooth-scroll du-scrollspy offset='40'><i class='fa fa-book'></i> <span class='hidden-xs'>Story</span></div>
      <div class='col-xs-2 about-nav-link' href='#about-works' du-smooth-scroll du-scrollspy offset='40'><i class='fa fa-gears'></i> <span class='hidden-xs'>Works</span></div>
      <div class='col-xs-2 about-nav-link' href='#about-team' du-smooth-scroll du-scrollspy offset='40'><i class='fa fa-group'></i> <span class='hidden-xs'>Team</span></div>
      <div class='col-xs-2 about-nav-link' href='#about-press' du-smooth-scroll du-scrollspy offset='40'><i class='fa fa-newspaper-o'></i> <span class='hidden-xs'>Press</span></div>
      <a class='col-xs-2 about-nav-link' href='/guidelines'><i class='fa fa-question-circle'></i> <span class='hidden-xs'>Guidelines</span></a>
      <a class='col-xs-2 about-nav-link' href='/contact'><i class='fa fa-phone'></i> <span class='hidden-xs'>Contact</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id='about-story'>
  <div class='container'>

    <h2 class="section-title" style='margin-bottom:10px'>Our Story</h2>
    <p class='section-description' style='margin-bottom:2em'><%= ENV.fetch('APP_NAME') %> is a social impact startup dedicated to bringing together communities to diffuse what works in education so that all learners can reach their full potential.</p>

    <div class='row' style='margin-bottom:20px'>
      <div class='col-md-5'>
        <%= image_tag "about/teachers.jpg", width: '100%' %>
      </div>

      <div class='col-md-7'>
        <p class='text-large text-left'>While innovative ideas, practices and tools have the potential to transform learning for all students and close the achievement gap, many of these are not sticking or spreading beyond a few pockets of excellence. Sevenzo provides a space where educators can openly exchange promising practice, translate that practice into personal action and test that practice in a safe environment with the support of other like-minded people.</p>

        <p class='text-large text-left'>The Sevenzo model was first piloted in 2015 through the Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation as the <%= link_to 'Redesign Challenge', 'https://redesignchallenge.org', target: '_blank' %>, engaging thousands of educators from across the country around a problem of practice. Founded in Pittsburgh in 2016, the new organization is building on the early traction of this pilot. Join us to bring educators together around the biggest challenges and most promising ideas in education.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div id='about-works'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='row'>
      <div class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1'>

        <h2 class="section-title" style='margin-bottom:10px'>What we do</h2>
        <p class='section-description' style='margin-bottom:2em'>We challenge this community to come together around issues that deeply impact studentsâ€™ ability to learn and thrive.</p>

        <div class='row'>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="center-block text-center"><i class="fa fa-comments fa-5x text-link"></i></div>
            <h2 class='lead text-center'>Build Community.</h2>
            <p class='text-center'>We bring people like you into an online conversation around issues that matter to young people.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="center-block text-center"><i class="fa fa-lightbulb-o fa-5x text-link"></i></div>
            <h2 class='lead text-center'>Find Bright Spots.</h2>
            <p class='text-center'>We crowdsource promising approaches and work with educators to turn them into recipes others can try.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="center-block text-center"><i class="fa fa-group fa-5x text-link"></i></div>
            <h2 class='lead text-center'>Spread What Works.</h2>
            <p class='text-center'>We run programs that support educators to try out and adapt those promising approaches to their own context.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id='about-team'>
  <div class='container'>

    <h2 class='section-heading'>Our Team</h2>
    <% t('about.team').each do |person| %>
      <div class="media media-team">
        <div class='media-left'><%= image_tag "about/team/#{person[:key]}.png", class: 'img-circle' %></div>
        <div class="media-body">
          <h3 class="media-heading">
            <%= person[:name] %>, <small><%= person[:title] %></small>
            <br class='visible-xs'>
            <small class='pull-right hidden-xs'>
              <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-twitter'></i>".html_safe, person[:twitter], target: '_blank', class: 'tooltip-hover', title: "@#{person[:twitter].split('/').last}", data: {toggle: 'tooltip', placement: 'top'} %>
              &nbsp;
              <%= mail_to person[:email], "<i class='fa fa-envelope'></i>".html_safe, target: '_blank', class: 'tooltip-hover', title: person[:email], data: {toggle: 'tooltip', placement: 'top'} %>
              &nbsp;
              <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-linkedin'></i>".html_safe, person[:linkedin], target: '_blank' %>
            </small>
            <small class='visible-xs'>
              <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-twitter'></i>".html_safe, person[:twitter], target: '_blank', class: 'tooltip-hover', title: "@#{person[:twitter].split('/').last}", data: {toggle: 'tooltip', placement: 'top'} %>
              &nbsp;
              <%= mail_to person[:email], "<i class='fa fa-envelope'></i>".html_safe, target: '_blank', class: 'tooltip-hover', title: person[:email], data: {toggle: 'tooltip', placement: 'top'} %>
              &nbsp;
              <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-linkedin'></i>".html_safe, person[:linkedin], target: '_blank' %>
            </small>
          </h3>
          <div class='clearfix'></div>
          <p><%= person[:bio].html_safe %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <hr class='short'>

    <h2 class='section-heading'>Our Board</h2>
    <% t('about.board').each_slice(4) do |people| %>
      <div class='row row-advisors'>
        <% people.each do |person| %>
          <div class='col-md-4 text-center'>
            <%= link_to image_tag("about/board/#{person[:key]}.png", class: 'img-circle', width: '100px'), '#', data: { toggle: 'modal', target: "#board-#{person[:key]}" } %>

            <h4>
              <%= link_to person[:name], '#', data: { toggle: 'modal', target: "#board-#{person[:key]}" } %><br>
              <small>
                <%= person[:title] %>
                <br>
                <%= person[:organization] %>
              </small>
            </h4>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <hr class='short'>

    <h2 class='section-heading'>Our Advisors</h2>
    <% t('about.advisors').each_slice(4) do |people| %>
      <div class='row row-advisors'>
        <% people.each do |person| %>
          <div class='col-md-3 col-sm-6'>
            <div class="media">
              <div class='media-left'>
                <%= link_to image_tag("about/advisors/#{person[:key]}.png", class: 'img-circle', style: 'width:60px'), person[:link], target: '_blank' %>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h4 class="media-heading">
                  <%= link_to person[:name], person[:link], target: '_blank' %><br>
                  <small>
                    <%= person[:title] %>
                    <br>
                    <%= person[:organization] %>
                  </small>
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <hr class='short'>

    <h2 class='section-heading'>With Support From</h2>
    <% t('about.partners').each_slice(3) do |partners| %>
      <div class='row row-advisors'>
        <% partners.each do |partner| %>
          <div class='col-md-4 col-sm-6'>
            <div class="center-block text-center">
              <%= link_to image_tag("about/partners/#{partner[:key]}.png", width: '75%'), partner[:link], target: '_blank' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div id='about-press'>
  <div class='container'>

    <h2 class="section-title" style='margin-bottom:10px'>In the News</h2>

    <div id="carousel-press" class="carousel slide" data-interval='false'>

      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <% t('about.press').each_with_index do |press, index| %>
          <li data-target="#carousel-campaigns" data-slide-to="<%= index %>" class="<%= 'active' if index.zero? %>">
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ol>

      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <% t('about.press').each_with_index do |press, index| %>
          <div class='item <%= 'active' if index.zero? %>'>
            <div class='well well-white center-block text-center'>

              <blockquote class='quote'>
                <div>"<%= press[:snippet].html_safe %>"</div>
                <footer class='text-center'>
                  <%= "#{press[:publication]}. #{link_to press[:date], press[:link], target: '_blank'}".html_safe %>
                </footer>
              </blockquote>

            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-press" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
      </a>
      <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-press" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div id='about-cta'>
  <div class='container'>

    <h2 class="section-title text-submit">Know someone who may want to add to the discussion?</h2>
    <p class='section-description'>The more the merrier! Share our platform to help us get the best suggestions from educators like you.</p>

    <%= render partial: 'layouts/share_links', locals: { url: root_url, hashtag: ENV.fetch('COMPANY_NAME'), tweet: "#{ENV.fetch('APP_NAME')} is LIVE! Are you an innovative educator? Join us!", title: "Join #{ENV.fetch('APP_NAME')}!", description: "Are you an innovative educator? Then help revolutionize how educators across America come together to reimagine innovation in K-12 teaching and learning.", subject: "Join me on #{ENV.fetch('APP_NAME')}!" }, cache: true %>

    <div class='center-block text-center'>
      <a href="<%= ENV.fetch('TWITTER_URL') %>" class="twitter-follow-button" data-show-count="true" data-size="large">Follow @<%= ENV.fetch('TWITTER_URL').split('/').last %></a>

      <div class="fb-like" data-href="<%= ENV.fetch('FACEBOOK_URL') %>" data-width="300" data-layout="standard" data-action="like" data-show-faces="true" data-share="true" style='top:10px'></div>
      <script>!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],p=/^http:/.test(d.location)?'http':'https';if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src=p+'://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js';fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document, 'script', 'twitter-wjs');</script>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<% t('about.board').each do |person| %>
  <div class="modal fade" id="<%= "board-#{person[:key]}" %>">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
          <div class='text-large text-center'><%= person[:name] %></div>
        </div>
        <div class='modal-body'>
          <p><%= person[:bio].html_safe %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
